text: Tamil Nadu State Highway 10 (SH-10) connects Cuddalore with Chinnasalem. The total length of SH-10 is 102 km. SH-10 Route: Cuddalore - Kullanchavadi - Kurinjipadi - Vadalur - Neyveli - Vridhachallam - Veppur - Chinnasalem ==External links== * Cuddalore-Salem State Highway Map Category:State highways in Tamil Nadu
title: State Highway 10 (Tamil Nadu)
